== About Me
- I received my B.Sc. degree in Electrical and Computer Engineering from the [https://www.iut.ac.ir/en Isfahan University of Technology (IUT)], Isfahan, Iran, in 2016.
- I am working towards my PhD degree under the supervision of [https://msol.people.uic.edu Prof. Mojtaba Soltanalian] at the Department of Electrical and Computer Engineering (ECE), 
[https://uic.edu University of Illinois at Chicago (UIC)], Chicago, IL, USA.
- I was the recipient of the prestigious Wexler Award for 2016-2017. 

== Research 
My research interests include Optimization Theory, Statistical Signal Processing, Machine Learning, and their applications.
- Optimization Theory
- Statistical Signal Processing
- Machine Learning
- Theory of Deep Learning
- Model-Based Deep Learning
- Radar Signal Processing

